snippet.title: Monsters Inc. Wreck Room Arcade - Eight Ball Chaos Intro
snippet.description:
Monsters Inc. Wreck Room Arcade was a series of PC games developed by Sapient Gaming.  The series consisted of three games, with a fourth one that was only playable if one had the other three games installed.  The games were released on a daily basis from January 25, 2002 to January 27, 2002.

This is the intro to the second game in the series, Eight Ball Chaos.
